1. Install nodejs (npm)
    https://nodejs.org/en/
2. Install @ancular/cli - https://angular.io/guide/setup-local
    npm install -g @angular/cli
3. Create project
    ng new my-project-name
        type checking- N
        routing - N
        Use CSs

4. cd my-project-demo
5. npm start
    localhost:4200

6. src -> app -> app.component.html
    updated